description: Aspose.Cells for .NET is a spreadsheet programming component that allows software developers to manipulate and convert spreadsheet files from within their own applications. A combination of APIs and GUI controls, Aspose.Cells for .NET speeds up Microsoft Excel programming and conversion.
releaseNotes:
New Features
(CELLSNET-45695)- Set Number Format for Cells in Charts Data Table 
(CELLSNET-45666)- Get SheetId field of Excel Worksheet 
(CELLSNET-45664)- Reading and writing External connection of xlsb file. 
Enhancements
(CELLSNET-45660)- Sheet to Image rendering - alignment issue for Asian fonts 
Bugs
(CELLSNET-45408)- Value disappears or changes color when convert to pdf 
(CELLSNET-45696)- Slicer is not moving down in the sheet when inserting rows 
(CELLSNET-45675)- Error calculating the formulas (involving "SUMPRODUCT" and "TRANSPOSE") 
(CELLSNET-45651)- TextBox size changes when using Chinese font in the workbook in rendering to PDF
(CELLSNET-45678)- Partially missing characters when converting to image 
(CELLSNET-45667)- Trendline labels are not updated in MS Excel when we manually change the source value in the cells 
(CELLSNET-45620)- Color and interval between scale is different for 3D chart - Investigation required 
(CELLSNET-45397)- Aspose.Cells recognizes fonts in the chart incorrectly 
(CELLSNET-45700)- Excel 2016 Add-in pane removed from file after open/save in Aspose.Cells 
(CELLSNET-45693)- Worksheet is no more protected in the output file in SpreadsheetML to XLSX conversion 
(CELLSNET-45691)- Document is corrupted when re-saving it 
(CELLSNET-45690)- Styles seem to be carried over wrongly for some cells - SpreadsheetML to XLSX conversion 
(CELLSNET-45688)- Date column is not sorted correctly 
(CELLSNET-45687)- Worksheets protection properties are not carried from SpreadsheetML
(CELLSNET-45683)- SpreadsheetML AllowSort element doesn't work in the output XLSX
(CELLSNET-45682)- MS Excel prompts an error message "Excel found unreadable content...."
(CELLSNET-45676)- Document is corrupted when re-saving due to non-break space in worksheet name 
(CELLSNET-45673)- Alignment style applying for SpredSheetML 
(CELLSNET-45670)- Cells color is lost on converting to Image 
(CELLSNET-45692)- GridWeb does not ungroup rows on clicking the + button 
(CELLSNET-45654)- Comment added to the cell is not retrieved on client side - Aspose.Cells.GridWeb 
(CELLSNET-45645)- Exception occurs on opening the BUDGET RH 3_0.xlsm in GridWeb 
Exceptions
(CELLSNET-45657)- Input string was not in a correct format - Exception on Pivot.CalculateData() method 
(CELLSNET-45703)- Exception when converting XLSM file back to XLS file format
summary: Aspose.Cells for .Net is a class library for Excel document processing
title: Aspose.Cells for .NET
